2.1 The useCallback is a hook method which help reduce the number of time component will re-render. The useCallback have 2 parameters, function and dependencies. 
When using useCallback in the component it the first time it render, it will run the function normally. 
However in the next render, if the dependencies is remaining the same as first render, it will do nothing. The function in useCallback will re-render again when the dependencies change.

2.2 The code for unit test is in app.test.tsx file. It is only a concept of how I will write a unit test from provided code so it will not runable but just to display the test case for it.
